Panel

public static final int[] Panel
Attributes that can be used with a Panel.

Includes the following attributes:

AttributeDescription
org.panel:animationDuration Defines panel animation duration in ms.
org.panel:closedHandle Defines closed handle (drawable/color).
org.panel:linearFlying Defines if flying gesture forces linear interpolator in animation.
org.panel:openedHandle Defines opened handle (drawable/color).
org.panel:position Defines panel position on the screen.

See Also:
Panel_animationDuration, Panel_closedHandle, Panel_linearFlying, Panel_openedHandle, Panel_position
